OL,5,G2000 Bangers & Cash
OL,6,     FAston DB4/Tractor: Derek heads off
OL,7,     Fto Colchester to pick up a 1960
OL,8,     FAston Martin DB4 that has been
OL,9,     Fsitting under a tarpaulin in a
OL,10,     Fgarage that has collapsed round it
OL,11,     Ffor 40 years.
OL,12,G2100 Bangers & Cash: Restoring Classics
OL,13,     FA35/BMW Z3: The team take on one
OL,14,     Fof Derek's favourites - an Austin
OL,15,     FA35 - but its age ensures some
OL,16,     Fhefty bills. To bank some cash,
OL,17,     Ftheir second project is a quick
OL,18,     Fflip - a 1999 BMW Z3.
